always_ignore_confirmation.message: Ingabe ufuna isibambi sephasiwedi ukuthi sihlale siziba le webhusayithi?

extension_description.message: Isibambi sephasiwedi sisiza ukukuvikela ekuhlaseleni kobugebengu bokweba imininingwane ebucayi.

extension_detailed_description.message:
Uma ufaka iphasiwedi yakho ye-Gmail noma ye-Google for Work noma yikuphi kune-accounts.google.com, uzothola isaziso, ukuze uguqule iphasiwedi yakho uma kudingeka.

Inqolobane yephasiwedi iphinda izame ukuthola amakhasi angumgunyathi wokungena ngemvume we-Google ukuze akwazise ngaphambi kokuthi uthayiphe iphasiwedi yakho. Ukuze wenze njalo, Inqolobane yephasiwedi ihlola i-HTML yekhasi ngalinye olivakashelayo ukuze ibone uma ngabe izenzisa ikhasi lokungena ngemvume le-Google.

I-FAQ
-- Ingabe Inqolobane yephasiwedi izosebenza nini?
Inqolobane yephasiwedi izoziqalisa ngokwayo ngesikhathi esilandelayo lapho ufaka khona iphasiwedi yakho ku-accounts.google.com.

-- Ingabe Inqolobane yephasiwedi igcina iphasiwedi yami noma ukuthinta ukhiye -- esikhundleni salokho, igcina isithombe-mzwelo esivikelekile sephasiwedi yakho, eyisiqhathanisa nesithombe-mzwelo sokuthinta kwakho ukhiye kwakamuva ngaphakathi kwe-Chrome.

-- Ingabe Inqolobane yephasiwedi iyithumela kuphi idatha?
Uma usebenzisa Inqolobane yephasiwedi ku-akhawunti ye-Gmail, Inqolobane yephasiwedi ayithumeli noma iyiphi idatha kusukela kukhompuyutha yakho yasendaweni. Uma ngabe umqondisi wakho we-Google for Work akhetha ukuphakela Inqolobane yephasiwedi kusizinda sakho sonkana, umqondisi uzothola izaziso uma kuqala kusebenza Inqolobane yephasiwedi.

-- Yini imikhawulo Yenqolobane yephasiwedi?
Inqolobane yephasiwedi ayivikeli amawindi we-incognito, izinhlelo zokusebenza ze-Chrome, noma izandiso ze-Chrome. Futhi ayivikeli amaphasiwedi kumasevisi okungewona we-Google. Inqolobane yephasiwedi isebenza kuphela ngaphakathi kwesiphequluli sewebhu se-Chrome uma i-Javascript inikwe amandla.

-- Ngingayithola kuphi eminye imininingwane?
Vakashela i-FAQ egcwele ku-LINK_TBD, noma ungabona sonke isisekelo sekhodi somthombo ovulekile ku-https://github.com/google/password- catcher.

Ngokufaka le nto, uvumelana ne-Imigomo Yesevisi ye-Google ne-Inqubomgomo Yobumfihlo eku-www.google.com/policies/

initialization_message.message: Ukuze isibambi sephasiwedi siqale ukusebenza, sicela ungene ngemvume ku-akhawunti yakho.

password_warning_banner_body.message: Iphasiwedi yakho ye-Gmail ivele yavezwa kukhasi lokungena ngemvume okungelona le-Gmail. Kuzomele usethe ngokushesha iphasiwedi yakho ukuze ugcine i-akhawunti yakho ye-Gmail ivikelekile. Futhi, sicela wenze isiqiniseko sokuthi iphasiwedi yakho ye-Gmail ayiphindi isetshenziswe kwamanye amasevisi.

phishing_warning_banner_body.message: Leli sayithi libonakala lisebenzisa inguqulo okungeyona yekhasi lokungena le-Google ukweba iphasiwedi yakho, ngakho-ke livinjiwe. Uma uqonda ukuthi leli sayithi lingalimaza ikhompyutha yakho, ungahle uvakashela leli sayithi kodwa sicela uqaphele mayelana nolwazi olithayiphayo.
